data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 2 story home tucked in a cul-de-sac located in Grayson, one of   the best neighborhood in Georgia. This well maintained home features big beautiful eat-in  island kitchen that overlooks the family room but still flows into the formal living and dining  room. Some of the other features are crown molding, white kitchen cabinets, stainless steel  appliance, hardwood floors, gas log fireplace in family room. Still on the main level there is   a large bedroom and a full bath which is ideal guests. Upstairs, you'll find the serene   oversize master suit offering a peaceful retreat after a long day. The master suite features  a sitting area off the master bedroom, large walk in closet and double vanity in master bath.  Enjoy the economical convenience of very low utility bill due to the recently installed solar   panel system. Nothing to do but move into this 6 bedrooms and 4 baths home after closing.
